'''Australian Screen Online''' is an [[on-line database]] operated by the Australian [[National Film and Sound Archive]]. It provides information about and excerpts from a wide selection of Australian feature films, documentaries, television programs, newsreels, short films, animations, and home-movies. It also includes teachers' notes.<ref>http://aso.gov.au/about/</ref>
