The '''''Barlings Chronicle''''' is an important late 13th or early 14th century [[Latin]] [[chronicle]] from the [[Premonstratensian]] [[Barlings Abbey]] in [[Lincolnshire]], England.<ref>{{emc1|Julia Marvin|Barlings and Hagneby Chronicles|143}}</ref> It is closely related to the [[Hagnaby Chronicle]].
