us Ruralis'' ("Rural Dean") *'''DS''' &ndash; ''Deus'' ("God") *'''D.Se.''' &ndash; ''Doctor Scientiarum'' ("Doctor of Sciences") *'''D.V.''' &ndash; ''Deo Volente'' ("God willing") *'''Dupl.''' &ndash; ''Duplex'' ("Double feast" — Breviary) *'''Dupl. Maj.''' &ndash; ''Duplex Major'' ("Double Major feast") *'''Dupl. I. Cl.''' &ndash; ''Duplex Primæ Classis'' ("Double First Class feast" — Breviary) *'''Dupl. II. Cl.''' &ndash; ''Duplex Secundae Classis'' ("Double Second Class feast" — Breviary)
